    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*我们的游戏在上线时将不提供简体中文版本。不过，我们会关注愿望单的数量，并根据需求优先安排翻译。如果你希望看到简体中文版，请务必将游戏加入愿望单！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/32eea024f8e167b802457912641e3899.poster.avif?t=1770409696\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/32eea024f8e167b802457912641e3899.webm?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/32eea024f8e167b802457912641e3899.mp4?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Tattoo Removal Simulator》中,你将扮演一位技艺高超的纹身清除专家.故事发生在繁华都市中的一家小型工作室, 所有前来的客户都有一个共同的目标:抹去他们过去的片段——那些被色彩斑斓的图案、文字、秘密与故事所标记的痕迹.从轻松幽默、黑色笑话到充满戏剧、爱与喜悦的人生经历,每一个纹身都讲述着一段独特的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/63931fc03e7f30bcbde7d6d8bbb95060.poster.avif?t=1770409696\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/63931fc03e7f30bcbde7d6d8bbb95060.webm?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/63931fc03e7f30bcbde7d6d8bbb95060.mp4?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在去除精致纹身的过程中，享受揭示洁净肌肤的满足感，同时发现每个纹身背后的个人故事。节奏舒缓，让你沉浸在平静的清除过程中。但要小心疼痛值——若让客户感到太多不适，你将损失收入！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/ab805981345530a13e34c25dd09197b3.poster.avif?t=1770409696\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/ab805981345530a13e34c25dd09197b3.webm?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/ab805981345530a13e34c25dd09197b3.mp4?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生涯模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立并管理你的纹身清除工作室。使用平板查找客户、记录他们的故事。通过高质量的操作赚钱；失误将导致罚款和客户不满。升级你的工作室，购买新设备，解锁从基础激光到未来感十足的等离子激光等先进工具，让你的事业蒸蒸日上。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>休闲模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入一个轻松自在的游戏体验。随机客户与趣味纹身清除过程等待着你。没有压力，没有惩罚，只需享受清除墨迹的过程。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的工作室中体验独特又充满未知的故事。有些可能带你前往奇特的地点，有些可能被突如其来的事件打断。沉浸其中，看看这些故事将如何展开！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个每个纹身都诉说故事、每次清除都带来宁静与满足的世界中，探索纹身清除的艺术——一款融合放松、叙事与转变的游戏体验。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持VR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带上VR设备，获得更沉浸式的体验。全程支持虚拟现实，让每一个瞬间都更真实、更刺激、更令人难忘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/363d03234dd32951f3b5e155bfdba8fe.poster.avif?t=1770409696\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/363d03234dd32951f3b5e155bfdba8fe.webm?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143910/extras/363d03234dd32951f3b5e155bfdba8fe.mp4?t=1770409696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
